The title is a play on words and means as much as "Ass in the Hips". The artist calls himself johnny, apparently like many others. Tagging him would probably only lead to confusion. His circle tag would be the better tagging choice.

And I just noticed that his pixiv has all the pics in digital quality. And his print quality is rather low. Well fuck. What a waste of time.
